= DESCRIPTION

FFI port of Johnson.

= REQUIREMENTS

* Latest ruby-ffi from kenai repo

$ hg clone https://kenai.com/hg/ruby-ffi~mercurial 

* Latest jruby from kenai repo

$ git clone git://kenai.com/jruby~main jruby
$ cd jruby
$ ant
$ ant jar-complete

* Latest jsapi from mozilla repo

$ hg clone http://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/file/tip mozilla-src
$ cd mozilla-src/js/src
$ ./configure  --enable-debug --enable-gczeal
$ make
$ [sudo] make install

= USAGE

To work with FFI first do:

$ export JOHNSON_FFI=1

To run tests/autotest:

# with MRI Ruby

$ rake test
$ autotest

# with JRuby

$ jruby -S rake test
$ jruby -S autotest
